# Cursor Rules - Active Games World

## Project Overview
This is a Next.js 15 copy of activegamesworld.com (WordPress/Elementor).
The site is a one-page marketing site for interactive gaming franchise.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- React 19
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion

## Important Files
- `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` - Full project context (READ FIRST)
- `src/app/page.tsx` - Main page with i18n
- `src/components/` - All UI components
- `src/i18n/locales/` - Translations (en, fr, he)
- `src/data/games.ts` - Game data + original asset URLs

## Styling Guidelines
- Use Tailwind classes
- Custom neon effects in globals.css
- Colors: primary (#00f0ff), secondary (#ff00ff), dark (#0a0a0a)

## Languages
- English (en) - LTR
- French (fr) - LTR  
- Hebrew (he) - RTL

## Commands
- `npm run setup` - Download assets + start dev server on port 3003
- `npm run download` - Download assets only
- `npm run dev:3003` - Start dev server on port 3003

